data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom home it's just perfect for your family. Front and back yard completed with low maintenance. The backyard has turf, concrete and 2 mature trees, and raised walls for privacy. Home is ENERGY CERTIFY, Turn on your refrigerated AC without thinking on the electrical bill, SOLAR PANELS will be paid off at closing with the sale. This home has no carpet and all windows have beautiful wood shutters. Enjoy the park that's a block away, the gym, Albertsons, Vista Market, pharmacies, restaurants, gas stations and schools. This home has 2 car garage with opener. Home is ready and waiting for you and your family.
